@Banco_HostAddress = http://localhost:5121

### Documentação OpenAPI (Swagger)
GET {{Banco_HostAddress}}/swagger/v1/swagger.json
Accept: application/json

### Cadastro
POST {{Banco_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria Silva",
  "email": "maria@exemplo.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### Login (retorna JWT)
POST {{Banco_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "maria@exemplo.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### Listar contas (requer Bearer)
GET {{Banco_HostAddress}}/api/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Extrato (requer Bearer)
GET {{Banco_HostAddress}}/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
